videos.description: Kimani Lawrence gets the dunk and the foul on the fast break flexes on the Oregon defense.
videos.headline: ASU's Lawrence gets hyped after and-1 dunk

videos.description: Payton Pritchard races and pulls from deep to bank a 3-pointer to beat the halftime buzzer with the defense draped all over him.
videos.headline: Oregon's Pritchard banks deep contested 3 to beat halftime buzzer

videos.headline: Martin pass sets up Cheatham dunk
